"113","This rarely recorded ant (southern England and the west coast of Wales) is a social parasite of other species in the genus (especially M. sabuleti). Despite some insight, there is too little data to be confident in the biological and ecological requirements of the species.","Insufficient data were available to reach a supportable conclusion on the threat status for this taxon."
